  "id": "api/common/NgStyle",
  "title": "NgStyle",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/common/src/directives/ng_style.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L10-L85\" aria-label=\"建议修改\" title=\"建议修改\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/common/src/directives/ng_style.ts#L10-L85\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/common\", \"name\": \"@angular/common\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/common/NgStyle\", \"name\": \"NgStyle\" } }\n        ]\n      }\n    </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> / <a href=\"api/common\">@angular/common</a>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"ngstyle\">NgStyle<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgStyle#ngstyle\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label directive\">directive</label>\n    \n    \n    <label class=\"api-status-label stable\">稳定</label>\n    \n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <p class=\"short-description\"></p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Update an HTML element styles.</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\">修改 HTML 元素的样式。</p>\n<p></p>\n  \n\n  \n\n  <section class=\"directive-overview\">\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a>({ selector: '[<a href=\"api/common/NgStyle\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngStyle</a>]' })\nclass <a href=\"api/common/NgStyle\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgStyle</a> implements <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/DoCheck\">DoCheck</a> {\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/common/NgStyle#ngStyle\">set ngStyle: {...}</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/common/NgStyle#ngDoCheck\">ngDoCheck()</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n</section>\n\n  \n\n  \n  \n<section class=\"selectors\">\n  <h2 id=\"selectors\">选择器<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgStyle#selectors\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading selector\">\n  [<a href=\"api/common/NgStyle\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngStyle</a>]\n  </code-example>\n</section>\n\n\n  \n<section class=\"inputs\">\n  <h2 id=\"输入参数\">输入参数<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgStyle#输入参数\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n  <div class=\"input\">\n    <code><a href=\"api/common/NgStyle\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngStyle</a></code> 绑定到 <code><a href=\"api/common/NgStyle#ngStyle\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgStyle.ngStyle</a></code>\n    \n  </div>\n  \n</section>\n\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgStyle#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-origin=\"off\">The styles are updated according to the value of the expression evaluation:</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\">这些样式会根据表达式的求值结果进行更新：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">keys are style names with an optional <code>.&#x3C;unit></code> suffix (ie 'top.px', 'font-style.em'),</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\">key 是样式名，可以带一个可选的 <code>.&#x3C;unit></code> 后缀（比如 'top.px', 'font-style.em'），</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\">values are the values assigned to those properties (expressed in the given unit).</p>\n<p translation-result=\"\">value 是一些与这些属性相关的值（以指定的单位表示）。</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n\n</section>\n\n\n  \n\n\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n\n<section class=\"instance-properties\">\n  <h2 id=\"属性\">属性<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgStyle#属性\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>属性名</th>\n        <th>类型</th>\n        <th>说明</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n    \n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td><a id=\"ngStyle\"></a>ngStyle</td>\n        <td><label class=\"property-type-label\"><code>{\n    [key: string]: string;\n}</code></label></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          \n          \n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    \n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</section>\n\n  \n\n<section class=\"instance-methods\">\n  <h2 id=\"方法\">方法<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgStyle#方法\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n    <a id=\"ngDoCheck\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table instance-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th>\n    <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n      <h3 id=\"ngdocheck\">\n        ngDoCheck()\n        \n      <a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgStyle#ngdocheck\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n      <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/common/src/directives/ng_style.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L59-L67\" aria-label=\"建议修改\" title=\"建议修改\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/common/src/directives/ng_style.ts#L59-L67\" aria-label=\"查看源码\" title=\"查看源码\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n    </div>\n  </th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    \n  \n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        \n\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" linenums=\"false\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">ngDoCheck()</code-example>\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"参数\">参数</h4>\n<p>没有参数。</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n    </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n</section>\n\n\n  \n\n  \n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">使用说明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgStyle#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <code-example>\n&#x3C;some-element [<a href=\"api/common/NgStyle\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngStyle</a>]=\"{'font-style': styleExp}\">...&#x3C;/some-element>\n\n&#x3C;some-element [<a href=\"api/common/NgStyle\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngStyle</a>]=\"{'max-width.px': widthExp}\">...&#x3C;/some-element>\n\n&#x3C;some-element [<a href=\"api/common/NgStyle\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngStyle</a>]=\"objExp\">...&#x3C;/some-element>\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - guide/ajs-quick-reference\n - guide/template-syntax\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/common\n - api/common/NgStyle#description\n - api/common/NgStyle#ngDoCheck\n - api/common/NgStyle#ngStyle\n - api/common/NgStyle#ngdocheck\n - api/common/NgStyle#ngstyle\n - api/common/NgStyle#selectors\n - api/common/NgStyle#usage-notes\n - api/common/NgStyle#属性\n - api/common/NgStyle#方法\n - api/common/NgStyle#输入参数\n - api/core/Directive\n - api/core/DoCheck\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/common/src/directives/ng_style.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L10-L85\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/common/src/directives/ng_style.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L59-L67\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/common/src/directives/ng_style.ts#L10-L85\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.1.0/packages/common/src/directives/ng_style.ts#L59-L67\n-->"
